Rules.InvariantScript:
Switch(true,
    IsBlank(Self.Text),
    false,
    !IsBlank(varNewVendorHeader.Vendor) && Self.Text = varNewVendorHeader.Vendor,
    false,
    true
)

// Material Document is the same as the Goods receipt number
ThisItem.MaterialDocument

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
With(
    {
        searchResults: If(
            IsBlank(txtGoodsReceiptSearchResultsFilter.Text),
            colGoodsReceiptSearchResults,
            Search(
                colGoodsReceiptSearchResults,
                txtGoodsReceiptSearchResultsFilter.Text,
                "MaterialDocument",
                "Vendor",
                "PurchaseOrder",
                "MovementType",
                "Material",
                "PostingDate",
                "Location"
            )
        )
    },
    SortByColumns(
        searchResults,
        Switch(
            varGoodsReceiptSearchAllSortByColumn,
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderGoodsReceipt.Text,
            "MaterialDocument",
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderVendor.Text,
            "Vendor",
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderPurchaseOrder.Text,
            "PurchaseOrder",
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderMovementType.Text,
            "MovementType",
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderMaterial.Text,
            "Material",
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderPostingDate.Text,
            "PostingDate",
            btnGoodsReceiptSearchResultsTableHeaderLocation.Text,
            "Location"
        ),
        varGoodsReceiptSearchAllSortOrder
    )
)

Rule.InvariantScript: conGoodsReceiptSearchAllFooter.Height + conGoodsReceiptSearchAllResults.LayoutMinHeight + conGoodsReceiptSearchAllFields.Height + conGoodsReceiptSearchAllButtons.Height + Self.PaddingTop + Self.PaddingBottom + Self.LayoutGap * 2 + 10

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
//Display recent search result items sorting according to table header buttons selected and searched on further based upon filter text input
With(
    {
        recentItems: If(
            IsBlank(txtGoodsReceiptRecentlySearchedCommandBarFilter.Text),//Filter text not entered
            Filter(
            'SAP Search Histories',
            'SAP Search Histories (Views)'.'My Recent SAP Search History',//Entity view that has filter logic to return user's search history records
            'Object Type' = 'Object Type (SAP Search Histories)'.'Goods Receipt'
        ),
            Search(//Search on text entered in filtered field
                Filter(
            'SAP Search Histories',
            'SAP Search Histories (Views)'.'My Recent SAP Search History',//Entity view that has filter logic to return user's search history records
            'Object Type' = 'Object Type (SAP Search Histories)'.'Goods Receipt'//Filter on object type goods receipt
        ),
                txtGoodsReceiptRecentlySearchedCommandBarFilter.Text,
                "mpa_name",
                "mpa_objectid"
            )
        )
    },
    SortByColumns(
        recentItems,
        Switch(
            varRecentlySearchedSortByColumn,//determine which field to sort by based upon the tabel header column value selected and stored in variable
            btnGoodsReceiptRecentlySearchedTableHeaderMaterial.Text,
            "mpa_objectid",
            btnGoodsReceiptRecentlySearchedTableHeaderDescription.Text,
            "mpa_name",
            btnGoodsReceiptRecentlySearchedTableHeaderLastSearched.Text,
            "mpa_lastsearchedon"
        ),
        varRecentlySearchedSortOrder//sort ascending or descending based upon value stored in variable
    )
)

!IsEmpty(
    Filter(
        'SAP Search Histories',
        'SAP Search Histories (Views)'.'My Recent SAP Search History',//Entity view that has filter logic to return user's search history records
        'Object Type' = 'Object Type (SAP Search Histories)'.'Goods Receipt'//Filter on object type material
    )
)
